{"tid":824474,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"識煮公仔面算唔算識煮野食？","createTime":"2018-09-17T05:43:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-17T06:43:22.000Z","uid":53272,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"421e239afc01aef12276202118749ef3eabd3c95","tid":824474,"uid":53272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T05:43:37.000Z","msg":"有個朋友話自己識煮公仔面<br />\n又識煎餃子（燶）<br />\n仲識得蒸公仔點心（唔用蒸架）<br />\n<br />\n之後話佢男朋友真係三生有幸<br />\n識到佢呢個識煮野食既女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n心諗<br />\n只少啲餃子係你自己包先學人講識煮野食啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到底係咪我對煮野食既定義同大眾唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5554c36f82f3241888ab9cb2d739b47990a604fc","tid":824474,"uid":60219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T05:46:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/eDItpxT53q8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FeDItpxT53q8&d=TSwAaO0jxYalLmdtM34jRwHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=9b86984f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/eDItpxT53q8</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e0e4ba95a7047d0275d9bbee0688dcdca843059","tid":824474,"uid":154054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T05:51:33.000Z","msg":"見好多港女成日po烚腸仔意粉show 自己廚藝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f13da0c551d4c54af3cfbdc80609a424a2580f0","tid":824474,"uid":53272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5554c36f82f3241888ab9cb2d739b47990a604fc","tid":824474,"uid":60219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T05:46:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/eDItpxT53q8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.